    <p>Maya Dance The­atre presents a dig­i­tal work that aims to raise aware­ness of the iso­la­tion and lone­li­ness ex­pe­ri­enced by the el­derly even when they live with their fam­i­lies. The pro­duc­tion in­cludes a dance film and a photo ex­hi­bi­tion, as well as in­ter­views with youth, se­niors and a so­cial worker.</p>
    <p>WHEN: Thu, 8pm</p>
    <p>INFO: www.mayadancet­he­atre.org/events/bcd-1a</p>


